本剧音乐由来自[[电子音乐|电音]]组合{{link-en|生存乐队|Survive (band)}}的麦克·斯坦（Michael Stein）和凯尔·迪克森（Kyle Dixon）创作<ref name="billboard music">{{cite web|title=''Stranger Things'' Co-Composer Shares the Story Behind 2016's Most Unlikely Musical Sensation|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/rock/7488050/survive-stranger-things-soundtrack-interview|publisher=''[[公告牌_(杂志)|Billboard]]''|language=en|date=2016-08-29|access-date=2016-08-31|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308010036/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/rock/7488050/survive-stranger-things-soundtrack-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>，大量使用了音乐[[合成器|合成器]]，并对[[让-米歇尔·雅尔|让-米歇尔·雅尔]]、[[橘梦乐团|橘梦乐团]]、[[范吉利斯|范吉利斯]]、{{link-en|哥布林乐队|Goblin (band)}}、[[约翰·卡本特|约翰·卡本特]]、[[乔吉奥·莫罗德尔|乔吉奥·莫罗德尔]]及法比欧·弗利兹（Fabio Frizzi）等诸多20世纪80年代的流行代表致敬。<ref>{{cite web|title=Stranger Things: 10 eerie electronic gems to hear if you loved the Netflix show|url=http://www.factmag.com/2016/08/06/stranger-things-playlist/|website=FACT Magazine: Music News, New Music.|language=en|date=|access-date=2016-09-05|archive-date=2016-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913132222/http://www.factmag.com/2016/08/06/stranger-things-playlist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

斯坦和迪克森把自己的歌曲《哀歌》（"Dirge"）加入了要呈给網飛预审的本剧[[預告片|预告样片]]中，还提到说本片主创搭档[[杜夫兄弟|杜夫兄弟]]就是生存乐队的乐迷。<ref name="billboard music"/><ref name="rs music">{{cite web|title='Stranger Things': Meet the Band Behind Show's Creepy, Nostalgic Score|first=Christopher|last=Weingarten|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/stranger-things-survive-talk-their-creepy-nostalgic-score-w431789|publisher=''Rolling Stone''|language=en|date=2016-08-01|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155740/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/stranger-things-survive-talk-their-creepy-nostalgic-score-w431789|dead-url=no}}</ref>当本剧的正式拍摄计划于2015年7月左右获得公司批准后，杜夫兄弟马上联系了生存乐队，询问他们是否还在继续从事音乐创作；这2个音乐人给剧组送去了几十首以前的作品，希望能使他们感兴趣，并为烘托剧中人物角色起到作用。<ref name="billboard music"/>这2人与剧组谈妥后，一方面开始与制作人员们一起筛选他们的旧作品，看看有哪些适合用作新剧的配乐；另一方面，他们也结合故事中的人物特点，创作新的音乐。<ref name="rs music"/>斯坦和迪克森在正式选角开始之前已受雇加入剧组，而他们的乐曲样品就在导演进行试音选角时作为背景音乐播放，帮助烘托了整个环节的气氛。<ref name="rs music"/><ref>{{cite web|title=An Interview With SURVIVE: The Mysterious Band Behind The Epic 'Stranger Things' Score|last=Thomas|first=Helen|url=http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/stranger-things-soundtrack-survive-interview|publisher=NME|language=en-GB|date=|access-date=2016-09-05|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011132951/http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/stranger-things-soundtrack-survive-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>全剧的主题曲就以一首斯坦早先创作的未发布作品为基调。剧组从送来的尝鲜曲目集中选出了这首歌作为开场曲，并认为对其适当地再加工效果会更好。<ref name="billboard music"/>

除原创音乐外，《怪奇物语》也使用了众多经典乐曲，其中包括[[冲撞乐队|冲撞乐队]]、[[快乐小分队|快乐小分队]]、[[Toto|妥妥乐队]]、[[新秩序_(乐团)|新秩序乐队]]、[[手镯合唱团|手镯乐队]]、{{link-en|异乡人乐队|Foreigner (band)}}、{{link-en|回音与兔人乐队|Echo and the Bunnymen}}、[[彼得·盖布瑞尔|彼得·盖布瑞尔]]和{{link-en|柯雷·哈特|Corey Hart (singer)}}的作品，还有来自橘梦乐团、约翰·卡本特和范吉利斯的作品采样片段。<ref>{{cite web|title=Unpacking the '80s nostalgia of the 'Stranger Things' soundtrack|first=Phillip|last=Mylnar|url=http://mashable.com/2016/07/25/stranger-things-soundtrack-netflix|work=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|language=en|date=2016-07-25|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211160433/http://mashable.com/2016/07/25/stranger-things-soundtrack-netflix/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pitchfork albums"/>冲撞乐队的《{{link-en|我该何去何从|Should I Stay or Should I Go}}》还特别入选本剧关键情节的背景音乐，如威尔在颠倒世界中试图与母亲乔伊斯等取得联络的一幕戏。<ref name="pitchfork albums"/>

==== 原聲碟 ====
《怪奇物语》第1季原声碟包含75首由斯坦和迪克森参与创作的歌曲，共分2卷，由[[湖岸娛樂|湖岸唱片]]发行。这2卷音乐先后在2016年9月10日和19日发布，各含[[數字發行|数码下载]]版和[[串流媒體|串流媒體]]版。<ref>{{cite web|first=Noah|last=Yoo|title=Inside the Spellbinding Sound of "Stranger Things"|url=http://pitchfork.com/thepitch/1266-inside-the-spellbinding-sound-of-stranger-things/|work=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]|language=en|date=2016-08-16|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214060846/https://pitchfork.com/thepitch/1266-inside-the-spellbinding-sound-of-stranger-things/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pitchfork albums">{{cite web |url=http://pitchfork.com/news/67214-netflixs-stranger-things-soundtrack-detailed/ |title=Netflix's ''Stranger Things'' Soundtrack Detailed |first=Evan |last=Minsker |website=Pitchfork Media |language=en |date=2016-08-10 |accessdate=2016-08-19 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308031218/https://pitchfork.com/news/67214-netflixs-stranger-things-soundtrack-detailed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[黑胶唱片|黑胶材质]]散装限量典藏版和盒装限量典藏版则于2017年7月发售。<ref>{{cite web |title="Stranger Things" Soundtracks Get Cool Vinyl Releases, Box Set |first=Sam |last=Sodomsky |url=http://pitchfork.com/news/72466-stranger-things-soundtracks-get-cool-vinyl-releases-box-set/ |website=Pitchfork Media |language=en |date=2017-03-24 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214060944/https://pitchfork.com/news/72466-stranger-things-soundtracks-get-cool-vinyl-releases-box-set/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年7月14日，{{link-en|都市外套|Urban Outfitters}}公司独家发售了一种磁带版本。磁带包装物以硬卡纸（cardboard）为特色，这是为了刻意模仿旧式的[[VHS|VHS]]磁带外形及其包装。<ref>{{cite web|title=The 'Stranger Things' Soundtrack Is Coming Out On A Cassette That Looks Like A Old VHS|last=Galbraith|first=Alex|url=http://uproxx.com/music/stranger-things-soundtrack-cassette-release/|publisher=Uproxx|language=en|date=2017-06-08|accessdate=2017-06-09|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214060900/https://uproxx.com/music/stranger-things-soundtrack-cassette-release/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第1季的2卷音乐都分别获得[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]{{link-en|葛萊美獎最佳影視原聲帶獎|Grammy Award for Best Score Soundtrack for Visual Media|最佳影视原声帶奖}}提名，但都未获奖。<ref>{{cite web |title=Stranger Things soundtracks score Grammy nods |first=Christian |last=Holub |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/12/06/stranger-things-soundtracks-grammy-nominations |publisher=''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |language=en |date=2016-12-06 |accessdate=2016-12-11 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214060910/https://ew.com/article/2016/12/06/stranger-things-soundtracks-grammy-nominations/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年10月20日，《怪奇物语》第2季原声碟数字版发售。第2季原声碟仍由斯坦和迪克森创作，包含34首歌曲，在美国由湖岸唱片公司发行，在海外由因瓦达唱片（Invada Records）公司发行。原声碟还计划以CD、[[黑胶唱片|黑胶唱片]]和磁带等实体形式发行。<ref name="S2SoundtrackSpin">{{cite web|title=Listen to a New Song From the Stranger Things Season 2 Soundtrack|first=Liza|last=Cantrell|url=https://www.spin.com/2017/10/stranger-things-season-2-soundtrack-new-song/|work=''[[Spin_(杂志)|Spin]]''|language=en|date=2017-10-12|accessdate=2017-10-12|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214060913/https://www.spin.com/2017/10/stranger-things-season-2-soundtrack-new-song/|dead-url=no}}</ref>斯坦和迪克森称第2季的创作引入了“一种新风格，并适当保留了旧基调… 我们为支撑故事而创造了新的音乐元素，但也仍想要忠实于第1季原声之格调。”专辑的第1首歌曲《漫步霍金斯》（"Walkin' in Hawkins"）于2017年10月12日发售。<ref>{{cite web|title='Stranger Things' Previews Season Two Soundtrack With Majestic New Song|first=Elisa|last=Leight|publisher=''Rolling Stone''|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/hear-majestic-new-song-from-stranger-things-season-two-w508515|language=en|date=2017-10-12|accessdate=2017-10-12|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615032122/https://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/hear-majestic-new-song-from-stranger-things-season-two-w508515|dead-url=no}}</ref>

